---
title: Baja Shrimp  with Mexican Rice
description: Salsa brings warm-weather vibes. It’s juicy and tangy, with a touch of heat, making it the perfect complement to crispy, Mexican-spiced shrimp. Served over top steamy yellow rice and finished with lime crema and salsa, this dish celebrates summer!
